            "paragraph": "<p>At Moon Ridge, style has never been limited to what you wear — it’s a way of living. That same spirit carries into <strong>Moon Ridge Home & Interiors</strong>, where the character, warmth, and authenticity of our brand come to life through interior design.</p><p><strong>Natalie Jo Wakefield</strong> has long loved interior design, and no matter how Moon Ridge grows, she will always take on a <strong>small number of design clients</strong> because she genuinely enjoys the work. Her approach begins with each client’s story, style, and rhythm of life — creating spaces that feel elevated, intentional, and unmistakably personal.</p><p>Just like our hats, every piece recommended reflects timeless quality, thoughtful design, and craftsmanship meant to last.</p><p>If you’re interested in home or office interior design, <strong>email me anytime at: </strong><a href=\"mailto:natalie@moonridgecompany.com\"><strong>natalie@moonridgecompany.com</strong></a><strong> </strong>and let’s start designing a space that’s uniquely yours.</p><p>If you’re interested in home or office interior design, I’d love to connect.</p>",
